title: Free Pub Crawl
description: Remove the guesswork from your Lima bar hopping plans with this guided pub crawl in the city's historic center. Along with a guide, head to three pre-vetted bars for great drinks and an even better time. Your tour includes a drink at each, with a focus on classic Lima drinks such as the Pisco sour or Pisco libre.
all_descriptions: Remove the guesswork from your Lima bar hopping plans with this guided pub crawl in the city's historic center. Along with a guide, head to three pre-vetted bars for great drinks and an even better time. Your tour includes a drink at each, with a focus on classic Lima drinks such as the Pisco sour or Pisco libre.

ItineraryThis is a typical itinerary for this productPass By:Lima, Lima, Lima RegionEvery Friday and Saturday we have our FREE PUB CRAWL. We visit two bars and a big club with 07 dance floors. In each bar you get a free shot and we have free pass for the club and a free cocktail for everyone. Let´s party with local people and other travelers. This event is FREE but it just basis on TIP. See you guys!

reviews.title: Great time and a lot of fun for free!
reviews.text: I booked this tour at the last minute and I had a lot of fun. I met a lot of travellers and we got free shots and free pass to a big club in Lima. This was more fun than I expected. I highly recommend to take this free pub crawl.

reviews.title: Fun Night Out with Friends
reviews.text: I joined the Free Pub Crawl with my friends, and it turned out to be a really fun night. The guides kept the group organized and made the atmosphere lively, while also taking us to some great local spots we wouldn’t have found on our own. It was a safe, well-run experience and a perfect way to enjoy Lima’s nightlife with friends.
